  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Trapped in the Forest is a surreal open world folk horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You awake in a mysterious forest that seems strangely familiar. Have you been here before? Is this a dream or a nightmare?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your survival skills to the test in this haunting and creepy survival-horror sandbox game! Chop down trees, forage for items, hunt for food and build your own base in a forest haunted by an ancient evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long can you survive for in the forest?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Trapped in the Forest is a surreal open world folk horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You awake in a mysterious forest that seems strangely familiar. Have you been here before? Is this a dream or a nightmare?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your survival skills to the test in this haunting and creepy survival-horror sandbox game! Chop down trees, forage for items, hunt for food and build your own base in a forest haunted by an ancient evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long can you survive for in the forest?</p>",
